## 1. Introduction

### 1.1 Purpose

This Software Requirements Specification (SRS) document provides a comprehensive description of the PrepWise AI Mock Interview Platform. It defines the functional and non-functional requirements, system architecture, and design constraints for the platform that enables candidates to practice interviews with AI, HR teams to manage recruitment, and administrators to oversee the system.

### 1.2 Scope

**Product Name:** PrepWise - AI Mock Interview Platform

**Product Description:** A full-stack SaaS platform that leverages artificial intelligence to provide realistic mock interviews, instant feedback, and recruitment management tools.

**Key Goals:**
- Enable candidates to practice interviews in a safe, AI-powered environment
- Provide HR teams with tools to manage job postings and evaluate candidates
- Offer administrators complete platform oversight and analytics
- Deliver real-time voice interactions using advanced AI technologies
- Generate detailed, actionable feedback to improve interview performance

**Benefits:**
- 24/7 availability for interview practice
- Cost-effective alternative to traditional coaching
- Standardized evaluation metrics
- Data-driven hiring decisions
- Scalable platform for enterprise use

