## 2. Overall Description

### 2.1 Product Perspective

PrepWise is a standalone web-based SaaS platform that integrates with:
- **Firebase** for authentication, database, and file storage
- **Google Gemini AI** for intelligent question generation and feedback analysis
- **Vapi AI** for real-time voice interview capabilities
- **Cloudinary** for video/media storage and delivery

### 2.2 Product Functions

The system serves three primary user roles:

**Candidates:**
- Create and manage profile
- Upload resume and skills
- Create mock interview sessions
- Conduct voice-based AI interviews
- View detailed feedback and analytics
- Track progress over time
- Download PDF reports

**HR/Recruiters:**
- Manage company profile
- Create and publish job openings
- Invite candidates to interviews
- Review interview recordings and transcripts
- Access candidate performance reports
- Shortlist and rate candidates
- Manage team members

**Administrators:**
- Manage all users (approve, suspend, delete)
- View platform-wide analytics
- Configure system settings
- Enable/disable features
- Monitor system health
- Manage subscriptions

### 2.3 User Classes and Characteristics

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Users] --> B[Candidate]
    A --> C[HR/Recruiter]
    A --> D[Admin]
    
    B --> B1[Job Seekers]
    B --> B2[Career Switchers]
    B --> B3[Students]
    
    C --> C1[Hiring Managers]
    C --> C2[Recruiters]
    C --> C3[Talent Acquisition]
    
    D --> D1[System Administrator]
    D --> D2[Platform Manager]
    
