### 5.4 Sequence Diagram - Complete Interview Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Candidate
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant API as API Routes
    participant Gemini as Gemini AI
    participant Vapi as Vapi AI
    participant DB as Firestore
    
    Note over C,DB: Interview Creation
    C->>UI: Create Interview
    UI->>API: POST /api/interviews/create
    API->>Gemini: Generate questions
    Gemini-->>API: Questions array
    API->>DB: Save interview
    DB-->>API: Interview ID
    API-->>UI: Interview created
    
    Note over C,DB: Interview Execution
    C->>UI: Start Interview
    UI->>Vapi: Initialize call
    Vapi-->>UI: Connection established
    UI->>C: Display question
    C->>Vapi: Voice response
    Vapi->>UI: Transcribed text
    UI->>DB: Save transcript
    
    Note over C,DB: Feedback Generation
    UI->>API: POST /api/ai/generate-feedback
    API->>Gemini: Analyze responses
    Gemini-->>API: Feedback data
    API->>DB: Save feedback
    DB-->>API: Feedback ID
    API-->>UI: Feedback ready
    UI-->>C: Display feedback
```

