## 6. Data Requirements

### 6.1 Entity Relationship Diagram

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USER ||--o{ INTERVIEW : creates
    USER ||--o{ SUBSCRIPTION : has
    USER ||--o{ COMPANY : creates
    COMPANY ||--o{ JOB : has
    JOB ||--o{ INVITATION : generates
    JOB ||--o{ APPLICATION : receives
    USER ||--o{ APPLICATION : submits
    INTERVIEW ||--|| FEEDBACK : generates
    COMPANY ||--o{ INVITATION : sends
    
    USER {
        string uid PK
        string email
        string displayName
        enum role
        enum status
        timestamp createdAt
        string resumeURL
        string companyId FK
    }
    
    COMPANY {
        string id PK
        string name
        string industry
        string createdBy FK
        timestamp createdAt
    }
    
    JOB {
        string id PK
        string companyId FK
        string title
        array techStack
        enum status
        timestamp createdAt
    }
    
    INTERVIEW {
        string id PK
        string candidateId FK
        string jobRole
        array questions
        array transcript
        enum status
        timestamp completedAt
    }
    
    FEEDBACK {
        string id PK
        string interviewId FK
        number overallScore
        array strengths
        array weaknesses
        timestamp createdAt
    }
    
    INVITATION {
        string id PK
        string jobId FK
        string candidateEmail
        enum status
        timestamp expiresAt
    }
    
    APPLICATION {
        string id PK
        string jobId FK
        string candidateId FK
        enum status
        timestamp appliedAt
    }
    
    SUBSCRIPTION {
        string id PK
        string userId FK
        enum plan
        number interviewsUsed
        timestamp currentPeriodEnd
    }
```

### 6.2 Data Dictionary

#### 6.2.1 Users Collection

| Field | Type | Description | Constraints |
|-------|------|-------------|-------------|
| uid | string | Unique user identifier | Primary Key, Auto-generated by Firebase |
| email | string | User email address | Required, Unique, Valid email format |
| displayName | string | User's full name | Required, Max 100 chars |
| role | enum | User role | Required, One of: 'candidate', 'hr', 'admin' |
| status | enum | Account status | Required, One of: 'active', 'pending', 'suspended' |
| skills | array | List of skills (candidates) | Optional, Array of strings |
| experienceLevel | enum | Experience level | Optional, One of: 'entry', 'mid', 'senior', 'expert' |
| resumeURL | string | URL to resume PDF | Optional, Valid URL |
| companyId | string | Associated company (HR) | Optional, Foreign Key to companies |
| createdAt | timestamp | Account creation time | Auto-generated |
| updatedAt | timestamp | Last update time | Auto-updated |

#### 6.2.2 Interviews Collection

| Field | Type | Description | Constraints |
|-------|------|-------------|-------------|
| id | string | Interview identifier | Primary Key, Auto-generated |
| candidateId | string | Candidate user ID | Required, Foreign Key to users |
| jobRole | string | Target job role | Required, Max 200 chars |
| techStack | array | Technologies | Required, Array of strings |
| experienceLevel | enum | Target experience level | Required |
| duration | number | Interview duration (minutes) | Required, One of: 15, 30, 45, 60 |
| questions | array | Interview questions | Auto-generated, Array of objects |
| transcript | array | Q&A transcript | Auto-populated, Array of objects |
| status | enum | Interview state | Required, One of: 'scheduled', 'in-progress', 'completed', 'cancelled' |
| startedAt | timestamp | Start time | Auto-set on start |
| completedAt | timestamp | Completion time | Auto-set on completion |
| recordingUrl | string | Video recording URL | Optional |

#### 6.2.3 Feedback Collection

| Field | Type | Description | Constraints |
|-------|------|-------------|-------------|
| id | string | Feedback identifier | Primary Key, Auto-generated |
| interviewId | string | Associated interview | Required, Foreign Key to interviews |
| overallScore | number | Overall performance score | Required, Range: 0-100 |
| communicationScore | number | Communication rating | Required, Range: 0-100 |
| technicalScore | number | Technical accuracy | Required, Range: 0-100 |
| problemSolvingScore | number | Problem-solving ability | Required, Range: 0-100 |
| strengths | array | List of strengths | Auto-generated, Array of strings |
| weaknesses | array | Areas for improvement | Auto-generated, Array of strings |
| improvementTips | array | Actionable advice | Auto-generated, Array of strings |
| aiAnalysis | string | Detailed AI analysis | Auto-generated, Max 5000 chars |

