## 8. Appendices

### 8.1 Class Diagram

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class User {
        +string uid
        +string email
        +string displayName
        +UserRole role
        +UserStatus status
        +string[] skills
        +string resumeURL
        +register()
        +login()
        +updateProfile()
    }
    
    class Candidate {
        +createInterview()
        +viewFeedback()
        +downloadReport()
        +trackProgress()
    }
    
    class HR {
        +string companyId
        +createJob()
        +inviteCandidate()
        +reviewCandidates()
        +shortlistCandidate()
    }
    
    class Admin {
        +approveHR()
        +manageUsers()
        +viewAnalytics()
        +configureSettings()
    }
    
    class Interview {
        +string id
        +string candidateId
        +string jobRole
        +Question[] questions
        +Transcript[] transcript
        +InterviewStatus status
        +start()
        +complete()
        +cancel()
    }
    
    class Feedback {
        +string id
        +string interviewId
        +number overallScore
        +number[] categoryScores
        +string[] strengths
        +string[] weaknesses
        +generate()
        +export()
    }
    
    class Job {
        +string id
        +string companyId
        +string title
        +string[] techStack
        +JobStatus status
        +create()
        +update()
        +close()
    }
    
    class Company {
        +string id
        +string name
        +string industry
        +create()
        +update()
    }
    
    User <|-- Candidate
    User <|-- HR
    User <|-- Admin
    Candidate "1" --> "*" Interview : creates
    Interview "1" --> "1" Feedback : generates
    HR "1" --> "*" Job : manages
    HR "*" --> "1" Company : belongs to
    Company "1" --> "*" Job : has
```

### 8.2 State Diagram - Interview Status

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Scheduled: Create Interview
    Scheduled --> InProgress: Start Interview
    Scheduled --> Cancelled: Cancel
    InProgress --> Completed: End Interview
    InProgress --> Cancelled: Abort
    Completed --> [*]: Feedback Generated
    Cancelled --> [*]
    
    note right of InProgress
        Recording audio
        Capturing transcript
        Monitoring duration
    end note
    
    note right of Completed
        Generate feedback
        Calculate scores
        Save to database
    end note
```

### 8.3 Technology Stack Summary

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|-------|------------|---------|
| **Frontend** | Next.js 16 | React framework with App Router |
| **Language** | TypeScript | Type-safe development |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | Utility-first CSS |
| **UI Components** | shadcn/ui | Pre-built accessible components |
| **State** | React Hooks | Local state management |
| **Auth** | Firebase Auth | User authentication |
| **Database** | Cloud Firestore | NoSQL document database |
| **Storage** | Firebase Storage, Cloudinary | File and media storage |
| **AI - Questions** | Google Gemini | Question generation, feedback |
| **AI - Voice** | Vapi AI | Real-time voice interviews |
| **Deployment** | Vercel | Serverless hosting |
| **Email** | Firebase/SMTP | Notifications |

### 8.4 API Endpoints Summary

#### Authentication
- `POST /api/auth/register` - Register new user
- `POST /api/auth/login` - User login
- `POST /api/auth/logout` - User logout
- `POST /api/auth/reset-password` - Password reset

#### Interviews
- `POST /api/interviews/create` - Create interview
- `GET /api/interviews/:id` - Get interview details
- `GET /api/interviews/list` - List user interviews
- `PATCH /api/interviews/:id/status` - Update status
- `DELETE /api/interviews/:id` - Delete interview

#### Feedback
- `POST /api/ai/generate-feedback` - Generate AI feedback
- `GET /api/feedback/:interviewId` - Get feedback
- `GET /api/feedback/:id/download` - Download PDF

#### Jobs (HR)
- `POST /api/hr/jobs/create` - Create job
- `GET /api/hr/jobs/list` - List jobs
- `PATCH /api/hr/jobs/:id` - Update job
- `DELETE /api/hr/jobs/:id` - Delete job

#### Candidates (HR)
- `POST /api/hr/invite` - Invite candidate
- `GET /api/hr/candidates` - List candidates
- `PATCH /api/hr/candidates/:id/shortlist` - Shortlist

#### Admin
- `GET /api/admin/users` - List all users
- `PATCH /api/admin/users/:id/approve` - Approve HR
- `PATCH /api/admin/users/:id/suspend` - Suspend user
- `GET /api/admin/analytics` - Platform analytics
- `PATCH /api/admin/settings` - Update settings

#### Media
- `POST /api/upload-resume` - Upload resume PDF
- `POST /api/upload-video` - Upload video recording
- `GET /api/view-resume/:userId` - View resume

### 8.5 Glossary

| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| **Candidate** | Job seeker using platform for interview practice |
| **HR/Recruiter** | Hiring professional managing jobs and candidates |
| **Mock Interview** | Simulated interview session with AI |
| **Feedback** | AI-generated analysis of interview performance |
| **Transcript** | Text record of interview questions and answers |
| **Shortlist** | HR-curated list of preferred candidates |
| **Tech Stack** | Set of technologies for a job role |
| **Experience Level** | Career stage: entry, mid, senior, expert |
| **Gemini** | Google's generative AI for text analysis |
| **Vapi** | Voice AI platform for real-time conversations |
| **Firestore** | Google Cloud NoSQL database |
| **RBAC** | Role-Based Access Control system |

